message.body: Hey Sofie, running a little behind, can we do 12?
Sure yes perfect where should we meet
And based in the bus schedule I think it will be more like 12:10
Great I'm on 4th floor gnna b reading text me when I should comedown

I had some great times with you, but I don't see things going anywhere and I don't have time for just hanging In between. To tell you the truth I'm still a little scarred from being locked out of your place naked for an hour and arriving to your place with no sheets on the bed. I just feel like everything was an omen from a bad night.
He made me do it... He was like I know, I'm busy too, but can I come over tonight... My first real break in a text... Thanks for the encouragement!
Haha, thanks!!! I almost ended it with don't feel bad, it's no you it's me, but I erased that because it's not me, it's him...
